Somebody, please help!

1040
01:29:45,687 --> 01:29:47,623
(CRYING) No!

1041
01:29:48,123 --> 01:29:49,591
No, please.

1042
01:29:49,625 --> 01:29:51,727
Help! Help!

1043
01:29:53,929 --> 01:29:55,030
(SCREAMS)

1044
01:29:56,765 --> 01:29:57,766
(GRUNTS)

1045
01:30:03,505 --> 01:30:05,439
(SCREAMS) Help!

1046
01:30:05,473 --> 01:30:06,942
(SCREAMING)

1047
01:30:08,043 --> 01:30:09,811
Help me, please!

1048
01:30:09,845 --> 01:30:11,647
- Help! (SCREAMING)
- (AX SLASHES)

1049
01:30:15,918 --> 01:30:17,451
(SCREAMS)

1050
01:30:20,756 --> 01:30:22,791
Please, no! No!

1051
01:30:23,558 --> 01:30:24,860
I won't tell anyone!

1052
01:30:24,893 --> 01:30:26,460
(SOBBING) Please, I swear!

1053
01:30:26,828 --> 01:30:28,563
No!

1054
01:30:28,597 --> 01:30:32,100
Please! I'll do anything
you want.

1055
01:30:32,134 --> 01:30:35,203
It's not about
what I want anymore, Mitsy.

1056
01:30:35,237 --> 01:30:36,171
MITSY: (CRYING) Please.

1057
01:30:36,204 --> 01:30:38,907
It's about making the best
of what I have.

1058
01:30:38,941 --> 01:30:41,777
MITSY: (SOBBING) No! No!

1059
01:30:42,945 --> 01:30:44,713
(SCREAMS) No!

1060
01:30:44,746 --> 01:30:46,447
(DOOR CREAKING)

1061
01:30:48,750 --> 01:30:50,585
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

