1067
01:33:32,848 --> 01:33:34,149
(SPEAKING GERMAN)

1068
01:33:45,427 --> 01:33:46,895
(MAGGOTS SQUIRMING)

1069
01:33:50,398 --> 01:33:52,767
(IN ENGLISH)
Bless us, O' Lord,

1070
01:33:52,801 --> 01:33:55,437
and these thy gifts

1071
01:33:55,470 --> 01:33:59,207
which we are about to receive
from thy bounty,

1072
01:34:01,042 --> 01:34:02,944
