1077
01:34:41,416 --> 01:34:42,851
(MAN SHOUTS INDISTINCTLY)

1078
01:34:43,519 --> 01:34:45,720
(SOLDIERS CHATTERING)

1079
01:34:45,754 --> 01:34:47,055
